>> source: Experimentation
>> time required: 6 minutes
>> servings: 1

Bring water to a boil.

Measure @coffee beans{15*%g} into the #coffee grinder{} and grind.

Use water to preheat #v60{} and #filter. Reboil water and throw out heating water.

Put @water{30*%g} in over ~{15%seconds} and wait for ~{30%seconds} to let it bloom.

Then continuously pour @&water{120*%g} over the next ~{30%seconds}.

Finally pour the last @&water{100*%g} over the next ~{30%seconds}.

Wait until drained and serve.
